<br>
Anyway, my suggestion.<br>
<br>
I know you have it cornered off so that the run of the mill peeps can't get into the officer boards... have you ever thought of doing that to the rest of the boards? Leaving a public general board, but making a fed-member only public board? <br>
<br>
/trys to pull together his scattered thoughts.<br>
<br>
The reason for such an action I believe are obvious. By reading past threads that digressed into basicly &quot;flame wars&quot; it seams that SOME of the most vocal people (or should that be peeps pointing fingures?) are not currently members of the Federation.<br>
<br>
Basicly give a place to work through your feuds without outside influences fanning the flames.<br>
<br>
I think I am going to end there, knowing my own tendency to write in ways that are perfectly understandable to me but no one else.<br>
<br>
