While i appreciated Vilenu coming to my defence I am less happy with the way that it was done.  I write the way i do in order te express my displeasure at a situation and not to point fingers.  I was trying to focus on the problem as I saw it rather than who did what to whom.  It could have been Steelfyst or Lachadan or Stragus who set up the situation and I would have used the same words in the same way.  <br>
<br>
This is a game.  I dont know many if any of you in RL.  I give less that half a rats ass what you do in RL.  I DO care what you do in game.  I DO CARE if you hurt my game family in any way shape or form.  Bringing in RL conflicts between people hurts my game family.  They have NO PLACE on this board.<br>
<br>
I am not saying that there will be no conflict between people.  This would be completly deluded on my part and totaly unrealistic.  I am just saying that if there is a RL conflict between people it should stay in RL.  We on the board dont need to know if Muratt has pink and purple pubic hair.  We dont need to know that Bissmark is into leather and bondage.  We dont need to know that Pickering goes out on weekends and gets drunk and stoned.  These things have nothing to do with gameplay and SHOULD BE KEPT SEPERATE!<br>
<br>
We need to stop the personal attacks on this board and we need to find a way to keep them from happening again.<br>
<br>
